{{info}}**Question:** Given the following XML document:
{{code}} <?xml version="1.0" ?> <object> <class> <name>XWiki.XWikiRights</name> <defaultWeb>Main</defaultWeb> <nameField/> <allow> <name>allow</name> <prettyName>Allow/Deny</prettyName> <unmodifiable>0</unmodifiable> <number>1</number> </allow> <groups> <name>groups</name> <prettyName>Groups</prettyName> <unmodifiable>0</unmodifiable> <number>3</number> </groups> <levels> <name>levels</name> <prettyName>Levels</prettyName> <unmodifiable>0</unmodifiable> <number>4</number> </levels> <users> <name>users</name> <prettyName>Users</prettyName> <unmodifiable>0</unmodifiable> <size>5</size> <number>6</number> </users> <groups> <name>groups</name> <prettyName>Groups</prettyName> <unmodifiable>0</unmodifiable> <size>5</size> <number>7</number> </groups> </class> </object> {{/code}}
Write the XPath selectors that return the following nodes: * The second child of the element after ##nameField## * All the elements that have the ##size## attribute * The sum of all the values inside the ##number## elements {{/info}}
